welcomeMessage:
Welcome %s,

Before you start adding your details we need to authenticate you.

Please select any one of the way from below to move forward.
defaultErrorDescription: Either it's you or it's us. Most probably its us only but please go back and retry, we have recorded this error and will soon be working on it. If the error persists please sends us a mail from your profile page.
noDataFoundError: We were not able to find any data, please try again.
dataMissing: Some of the required fields are empty.
somethingWentWrongImageUpload: Something went wrong while uploading the image. Please try again.
noPropertiesAvailable: No Properties is being added by anyone. You can initiative from your end. Click on the Add A Property button in bottom right
propertyPerks: Few perks for the renter to know about, if there
propertyAgreements: Agreement rules which the renter should know about before hand, if there
propertyImages: Please add images for the property
inApartment: An apartment or owner doesn't stay in the same place
kindOfRentalAllowed: What kind of renter is allowed?
propertyDetailsNotFound: We were not able to find the property details. Please try again. Or might be the data is deleted or corrupted from the other end. We will look into this.
pleaseTryAgain: Please try again. Something went wrong from our end.
localStorageIssue: Some issue while fetching the details from local storage. Please logout and login again. If issue persists please re-install the application or clear the storage manually. Sorry for the inconvenience. We have captured this issue and will be looking into this.
pleaseTellUsYourUserType: Please tell us are you a/an
noPropertiesAddedByYou: You haven't added any new property. Please add one and start looking for renters.
userProfileImage: Please select an image for your profile
locationSearchError: Please provide a search text or zip code or latitude and longitude. For better results you can provide all the values.
confirmAddToWishlistProperty: Do you want to add %s property to your wishlist?
confirmDeleteWishlistProperty: Do you want to delete %s property from your wishlist?
okayWithRent: Are you okay with the monthly rent of %s?
okayWithDeposit: Are you okay with the yearly deposit of %s?
